description: DEVELOPMENT SITE AT 16, 18-25 & 26 PARK CRESCENT & 77-81 PORTLAND PLACE- Demolition and redevelopment of 16 Park Crescent, 18-25 Park Crescent, 26 Park Crescent and partial demolition of 77-81 Portland Place including reinstatement of Grade I listed Park Crescent facade to create [1910 sqm] D1 floorspace and [76] residential units including the creation of [9] new mews properties within rear courtyard at Park Crescent Mews.
